jlirc is a Java API for communcation with the LIRC and WinLIRC daemons,
which are used to receive (and send) IR-sgnals.

Most applications would use the org.lirc.util.SimpleLIRCClient class, see its API
documentation.

For more information see the API documentation and http://jlirc.sourceforge.net/.


